Loretta Burroughs was sentenced to 55 years in prison for the murder and dismemberment of her husband Daniel . 
  Daniel was missing for six years before his remains were found at his wife's home in Ventnor, New Jersey . 
  She stabbed him to death and cut up his body with a knife and a saw . 
  She hid his remains in storage containers and dragged them with her when she moved three times in six years . 
  She was found guilty of first-degree murder in May 2013 . 
  Judge compared the murder to Al Capone's St Valentine's Day massacre . 
  Loretta told the court she killed her husband to avoid moving to Florida . 
 